in the street?

228
00:12:32,799 --> 00:12:33,639
Yeah!

229
00:12:33,639 --> 00:12:34,679
It's once in a blue moon.

230
00:12:34,679 --> 00:12:35,400
Come on!

231
00:12:37,039 --> 00:12:38,440
