239
00:12:54,750 --> 00:12:55,440
Hurry up!

240
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:56,279
Or it'll be over.

241
00:12:56,279 --> 00:12:56,925
Come on.

242
00:12:58,900 --> 00:13:00,425
If there is a righteous gentleman

243
