Excuse me.

256
00:13:22,475 --> 00:13:23,100
Coming through.

257
00:13:23,375 --> 00:13:24,250
He is the third scholar?

258
00:13:24,250 --> 00:13:24,925
Yeah.

259
00:13:25,750 --> 00:13:27,030
What is he talking about?
I don't understand.

260
00:13:29,725 --> 00:13:30,519
Thanks.

