271
00:13:49,125 --> 00:13:50,650
Up to the situation now,

272
00:13:51,275 --> 00:13:52,159
it's still because of

273
00:13:52,725 --> 00:13:54,240
the rebellious villain,

274
00:13:54,399 --> 00:13:55,879
Xu Xiao!

275
00:13:56,600 --> 00:13:57,639
